    <h1>Data Aggregator</h1>
    <p class="description">A company that collects, validates, and distributes business NAP data across hundreds of directories. Submit once, syndicate everywhere — the <strong>upstream source</strong> for most citations in the US market.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
